title: RICHEY EDWARDS No Thoughts To Forget (A Documentary By JSK).avi
description:
'RICHEY EDWARDS : No Thoughts To Forget' 
is a non-profit 90 minute documentary Edited, Produced & Directed by JSK; Jason Stuart Kamasz 

The film utilizes existing audio interviews with Richey's sister, Rachel Elias , Manic Street Preachers & Richey himself and is a chronological account of Richey's upbringing and youth; the formation and subsequent rise of Manic Street Preachers; Richey's artistic achievements; disappearance and enduring legacy through to the present day.
